descript.supplinf:
Source data was obtained from the Texas Department of Transportation and processed into a state-wide coverage by TNRIS.
Coastline: This coverage contains a detailed version of the Texas coastline, including bays and estuaries. It does not contain the 3-marine league line, which is the legal boundary separating state and federal ownership.
TPWD GIS Lab: TPWD compiled the attributes. For detailed information, see the attributes tab.
descript.purpose: This feature class is a component of TPWD 'base' data. 'Base' data includes current, statewide geospatial information intended to provide context for mapping purposes.
